#: ../../library/sys.rst:211
msgid ""
"Return a dictionary mapping each thread's identifier to the topmost stack "
"frame currently active in that thread at the time the function is called. "
"Note that functions in the :mod:`traceback` module can build the call stack "
"given such a frame."
msgstr ""
"Retorna um dicionĂˇrio mapeando o identificador de cada encadeamento "
"(*thread*) para o quadro de pilha mais alto atualmente ativo nesse "
"encadeamento no momento em que a funĂ§ĂŁo Ă© chamada. Observe que as funĂ§Ăµes no "
"mĂłdulo :mod:`traceback` podem construir a pilha de chamadas dado tal quadro."

#: ../../library/sys.rst:216
msgid ""
"This is most useful for debugging deadlock:  this function does not require "
"the deadlocked threads' cooperation, and such threads' call stacks are "
"frozen for as long as they remain deadlocked.  The frame returned for a non-"
"deadlocked thread may bear no relationship to that thread's current activity "
"by the time calling code examines the frame."
msgstr ""
"Isso Ă© mais Ăştil para fazer a depuraĂ§ĂŁo de impasses: esta funĂ§ĂŁo nĂŁo requer "
"a cooperaĂ§ĂŁo das threads em impasse e as pilhas de chamadas de tais threads "
"sĂŁo congeladas enquanto permanecerem em impasse (*deadlock*). O quadro "
"retornado para uma thread sem impasse pode nĂŁo ter nenhuma relaĂ§ĂŁo com a "
"atividade atual da thread no momento em que o cĂłdigo de chamada examina o "
"quadro."

#: ../../library/sys.rst:224
msgid ""
"Raises an :ref:`auditing event <auditing>` ``sys._current_frames`` with no "
